oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Dave Austin Job No. 16562
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:subject: Accounting; Hatch Show Print (Firm);
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Typed invoice for an order placed by Dave Austin for 200 two color window cards announcing Shindig in the Country and Aunt Minnie's Farm and Country Roads Park on July 4-6. Receipt indicates agreed price, size, order quantity, shipping location and description. To view the posters for this order see https://digi.countrymusichalloffame.org/digital/collection/hatch3/id/32013 and https://digi.countrymusichalloffame.org/digital/collection/hatch3/id/32012.
